<b>Approved Server Add-ons:</b><br />
<a href="http://files.tpgleague.org/dod_shared/TPG_Roster_Check.zip">TPG Roster Check</a> - requires MetaMod which frequently comes with your server
<p>
<u>Instructions For Use:</u><br/>
<br/>
Linux servers: <br/>
Create this folder and upload the .so file: /dod/addons/tpgroster/tpg_roster_check_mm_i386.so<br/>
Install MetaMod if it is not installed and modify this file: /dod/addons/metamod/plugins.ini<br/>
Add this line: linux addons/tpgroster/tpg_roster_check_mm_i386.so<br/>
<br/>
Windows servers: <br/>
Create this folder and upload the .so and .dll file:<br/>
/dod/addons/tpgroster/tpg_roster_check_mm_i386.so<br/>
/dod/addons/tpgroster/tpg_roster_check_mm.dll<br/>
Install MetaMod if it is not installed and modify this file: /dod/addons/metamod/plugins.ini<br/>
Add this line: windows addons/tpgroster/tpg_roster_check_mm_i386.so<br/>
<br/>
Command to use the TPG Roster Check:<br/>
rcon tpg_roster [Match ID]
